OL,3,CNew fears that more children were
OL,4,Cimpacted by Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FInvestigation by Amy Lewis and Senior
OL,7,FProducer Cat Dinneny
OL,9,FOver 30 families have come together
OL,10,Ffor the first time to demand answers
OL,11,Fabout their children's birth defects
OL,12,Fwhich they believe were linked to
OL,13,Ftoxic waste from the closure of
OL,14,FCorby's former steelworks.
OL,16,FThe scandal was the subject of the
OL,17,FNetflix series Toxic Town, and since
OL,18,Fit aired earlier this year ITV News
OL,19,Fhas been told 40 more families have
OL,20,Fcome forward to the solicitor
OL,21,Frepresenting the original families.
