OL,3,CNew fears that more children were
OL,4,Cimpacted by Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FThey include more than 10 whose
OL,7,Fchildren died as a result of the
OL,8,Fdefects.
OL,10,FThose impacted have called for North
OL,11,FNorthamptonshire Council to provide
OL,12,Fmore details on where the toxic waste
OL,13,Fwas dumped, as calls for a public
OL,14,Finquiry grow amid fears the waste is
OL,15,Fstill causing impacts to this day.
OL,17,F"There's got to be a reason why this
OL,18,Fhas happened."
