OL,3,CNew fears that more children were
OL,4,Cimpacted by Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FFor decades, Margaret Finlay has
OL,7,Fblamed herself for her baby daughter's
OL,8,Fdeath. Tortured by thoughts she could
OL,9,Fhave done more to protect her, she
OL,10,Feven tried to take her own life.
OL,12,FCarrie-Anne was born by emergency
OL,13,Fcaesarean at 29 weeks in 1988. She
OL,14,Fdied two days later, a post-mortem
OL,15,Fexamination revealing her lungs had
OL,16,Fnot developed properly.
OL,18,FWe met Margaret at The Steel Bar in
OL,19,FCorby, a music venue on the edge of
OL,20,Fthe town that shares a car park with
OL,21,Fthe local football club.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
