OL,3,CNew fears that more children were
OL,4,Cimpacted by Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FShe has come for a meeting, but told
OL,7,Fus she rarely leaves the house because
OL,8,Fof her panic attacks. "I've been ill
OL,9,Fever since my little girl was born,"
OL,10,Fshe said.
OL,12,F"There's got to be a reason why this
OL,13,Fhas happened. Babies don't just die,"
OL,14,Fshe added. "My other children are
OL,15,Fhealthy. To this day I can't cope. I'm
OL,16,Funder the doctor, I don't leave the
OL,17,Fhouse. There has never ever been an
OL,18,Fexplanation why and I blame myself."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
