OL,6,FShe has spent the last 30 years
OL,7,Fwondering what she could have done
OL,8,Fdifferently... until she watched the
OL,9,FNetflix series.
OL,11,FIt tells the story of a landmark court
OL,12,Fcase which linked birth defects to the
OL,13,Freclamation of Corby's steelworks.
OL,15,FThe plant was one of the largest in
OL,16,FEurope until it closed in the 1980s.
OL,17,FFor more than a decade, open-top
OL,18,Ftrucks with dust containing toxic
OL,19,Fchemicals were transported and dumped
OL,20,Fall over Corby.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
