OL,4,Cimpacted by Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FIn 2009, 18 families went to the High
OL,7,FCourt to successfully argue North
OL,8,FNorthamptonshire Council (then called
OL,9,FCorby Borough Council) had negligently
OL,10,Fdumped the waste, with airborne waste
OL,11,Ffrom the reclamation, resulting in
OL,12,Fmultiple birth defects.
OL,14,FNone of those attending were part of
OL,15,Fthe 2009 case with some of those
OL,16,Fpresent told they could not be part of
OL,17,Fthe original proceedings because their
OL,18,Fchildren had died.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
