OL,3,CNew fears that more children were
OL,4,Cimpacted by Corby toxic waste scandal
OL,6,FSince the Netflix series aired earlier
OL,7,Fthis year, more people in Corby, like
OL,8,FMargaret, have started asking
OL,9,Fquestions about whether the harmful
OL,10,Fwaste from the town's steelworks is to
OL,11,Fblame for their own deficiencies,
OL,12,Fmiscarriages and infant deaths.
OL,14,F"When I watched the series, it really
OL,15,Fshook me up," Margaret told us.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
