OL,6,F"My daughter said maybe that was what
OL,7,Fwas wrong with Carrie-Anne. I lived on
OL,8,FWestfields Road at the time, it's not
OL,9,Fthat far from the steelworks and my
OL,10,Fhusband worked in the steelworks as
OL,11,Fwell. I never even thought about
OL,12,Fputting the two and two together until
OL,13,FI saw the programme."
OL,15,FShe added: "It brought it all flooding
OL,16,Fback again, all the pain. The pain
OL,17,Fnever goes away, never ever. It
OL,18,Fdoesn't ease. Time doesn't heal, you
OL,19,Fjust live with it day in and day out.
OL,20,FIt's not just me in this situation.
OL,21,FThey need to admit it was their fault."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
