OL,6,F"I know I'm not alone."
OL,8,FMargaret was contacted by Tracey
OL,9,FTaylor who, similar to Margaret,
OL,10,Fworked next to the steelworks for
OL,11,Fyears. Her daughter, Shelby-Anne, died
OL,12,Fjust four days old with ear, heart,
OL,13,Fliver and lung deformities.
OL,15,FTracey provided crucial evidence in
OL,16,Fthe 2009 case but was ultimately
OL,17,Fexcluded because her daughter had
OL,18,Fpassed away. For Tracey, the 2009 case
OL,19,Fwas always the tip of the iceberg.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
