OL,6,FThat is what led her to organise a
OL,7,Fmeeting, bringing around 30 families
OL,8,Ftogether who have lost children or who
OL,9,Fhave deformities, and who think it
OL,10,Fmight be linked to the steelworks.
OL,12,FAddressing the crowd, who had gathered
OL,13,Fin a semi-circle at The Steel Bar, she
OL,14,Fsaid: "I've always known there's been
OL,15,Fmore angel babies, more people
OL,16,Faffected and more people's health
OL,17,Faffected than just the original 18
OL,18,Fthat were in the first court case.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
