OL,6,F"I did say to Des (Collins, the lawyer
OL,7,Fwho represented the families in 2009),
OL,8,FI know I'm not alone. But at that time
OL,9,Fthere wasn't social media and news
OL,10,Freports and papers like there are
OL,11,Ftoday."
OL,13,FTracey has spent the last five weeks
OL,14,Fsending out questionnaires to people
OL,15,Fwho had started airing their concerns
OL,16,Fonline after Toxic Town thrust the
OL,17,Fissue back into the news agenda.
