OL,6,FShe then invited dozens of them to a
OL,7,Fmeeting to share their stories
OL,8,Ftogether for the first time, and ITV
OL,9,FNews was also invited along. No one,
OL,10,Fapart from Tracey, was involved in the
OL,11,F2009 case.
OL,13,FTracey added: "It was very hard for me
OL,14,Fto be there with those 18 parents,
OL,15,Feven though they welcomed me with open
OL,16,Farms, knowing that I was there without
OL,17,Fa child and they all had their child.
OL,18,FAt the back of my mind and in my
OL,19,Fheart, I knew that there was more
OL,20,Fpeople out there who had angel babies
OL,21,Flike my Shelby-Anne."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
