OL,6,FIt was at this meeting that we also
OL,7,Fmet Aimee Duffy and her six-year-old
OL,8,Fson Thomas. He is missing fingers on
OL,9,Fone of his hands, his right leg is
OL,10,Fshorter than his left and one of his
OL,11,Ffeet is two sizes smaller than the
OL,12,Fother.
OL,14,FThomas Duffy was born with several
OL,15,Flimb deficiencies, and his mother
OL,16,Fwonders if waste from the steelworks
OL,17,Fis to blame
