OL,6,FThomas was born 30 years after the
OL,7,Fsteelworks closed, but having ruled
OL,8,Fout any genetic abnormality with
OL,9,Fvigorous testing over the last few
OL,10,Fyears, Aimee is wondering whether the
OL,11,Fland their house is built on is to
OL,12,Fblame.
OL,14,FShe said: "I live right next to Corby
OL,15,Fand I think maybe that's why Thomas'
OL,16,Fhand and arm is the way it is. Every
OL,17,Ftest has come back normal."
