OL,6,FITV News reporter Amy Lewis has been
OL,7,Ffollowing the story of families in the
OL,8,FCorby area who believe their health
OL,9,Fhas been affected by toxic waste
OL,11,FHer fears are exacerbated by the fact
OL,12,Fa whistleblower revealed to ITV News
OL,13,Fthat the toxic waste was dumped at
OL,14,Fmultiple sites across Corby, not just
OL,15,Fat Deene Quarry.
OL,17,F"There's a chance that where I live
OL,18,Fcould be built on toxic wasteland. I
OL,19,Fdon't know if it was dumped there."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/20
