OL,6,F"The people in Corby have not received
OL,7,Fjustice."
OL,9,FThe lawyer who represented the
OL,10,Ffamilies in the 2009 High Court case,
OL,11,FDes Collins, says he has been
OL,12,Fcontacted by around 40 families this
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,FHe is calling for a public inquiry,
OL,16,Fand pushing North Northamptonshire
OL,17,FCouncil to reveal all of the locations
OL,18,Fwhere the waste was dumped.
