OL,6,FHe told ITV News: "I think the people
OL,7,Fin Corby have not received justice. A
OL,8,Fsmall number of mothers who got
OL,9,Ftogether and fought this case did
OL,10,Freceive justice, but the people of
OL,11,FCorby were ignored completely.
OL,13,F"What we didn't have to establish (in
OL,14,F2009) was precisely where (the waste)
OL,15,Fwas moved to. In order to establish
OL,16,Fthat it's still causing problems, we
OL,17,Fhave to know where it is. This week
OL,18,Fwe've sent a third letter to the
OL,19,Fcouncil saying you've got to tell us."
